<p>The <i><b>Chicago Sun-Times</b></i> is an American daily tabloid published in <a href="Chicago,_Illinois" title="Chicago, Illinois" class="mw-redirect">Chicago, Illinois</a>. It is the flagship paper of <a href="Wrapports_LLC" title="Wrapports LLC" class="mw-redirect">Wrapports LLC</a> and its <a href="Sun-Times_Media_Group" title="Sun-Times Media Group">Sun-Times Media Group</a> subsidiary.</p>
